<div id="content">        <div class="spacer"></div>             <span id="shash-97315"><div class="post" id="post-97315">                    <h1><a href="http://trilema.com/2020/pimp-by-robert-beck-aka-iceberg-slim-adnotated-without-permission-chapter-4-a-degree-in-pimping/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Pimp. By Robert Beck aka Iceberg Slim. Adnotated without permission. Chapter 4 -- A degree in pimping.">Pimp. By Robert Beck aka Iceberg Slim. Adnotated without permission. Chapter 4 -- A degree in pimping.</a></h1>                        <div class="date">                                     Friday, 16 October, Year 12 d.Tr.&nbsp;|&nbsp;Author: <a href="http://trilema.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Mircea Popescu">Mircea Popescu</a>                                                        </div>

                        <div class="entry">
<p>When I got back to Milwaukee, Mama, and the street, my mind was straitjacketed into the pimp game.<sup><a href="#footnote_0_97315" id="identifier_0_97315" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="I seem to remember very similar claims last time he got out. Is it the case prison terms don't work, fundamentally, or is it the case he's trying to sell you the theory prison terms don't work, fundamentally ? What's your call, slick ?">i</a></sup> Back in the joint I had dreamed almost nightly. They were cruel players.</p>
<p>They were fantastic. I would see myself gigantic and powerful like God Almighty. My clothes would glow. My underwear would be rainbow-hued silk petting my skin.</p>
<p>My suits were spun-gold shot through with precious stones. My shoes would be dazzling silver. The toes were as sharp as daggers. Beautiful whores with piteous eyes groveled at my feet.</p>
<p>Through the dream mist I would see huge shaped stakes. The whores' painted faces would be wild in fear. They would wail and beg me not to murder them on those sharp steel stakes.</p>
<p>I would laugh madly. Springs of scarlet would spurt from their behinds as I joyfully booted them crotch first onto the sharp pikes. They would flop around like dying chickens. They would finally fall away in a welter of blood into two red halves.</p>
