<p>Those pimps back in the joint sure knew basic whorology. I was glad my ears had flapped to all those rundowns.</p>
<p>They had said, "Chase a whore, you get a chump's weak cop. Stalk a whore, you get a pimp's strong cop."<sup><a href="#footnote_12_97315" id="identifier_12_97315" class="footnote-link footnote-identifier-link" title="Indeed.">xiii</a></sup></p>
